data.description: Seller will credit Buyer up to $2,500 in Closing Costs on full price Offer closing before 1/31/24.  Home Warranty of America 13 mo. Home Warranty Coverage included.  Roof was recently inspected (report attached). The roof is a recently installed   dimensional weatherwood color shingle. The roof is in great condition.  Property could use some cosmetic upgrades, flooring, paint, etc. Priced accordingly.  Highly desirable 55+ golf cart friendly community, with access to a large menu of amenities including community indoor and outdoor pools, tennis courts, lawn bowling, and pickle ball to name a few.  Property is cosmetically distressed, needs paint, carpet/flooring upgrade, and landscaping.
